## Additional Terms for Health Data

While this software is licensed under the MIT License, users implementing this
software for handling health-related data must ensure compliance with:

- HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act) in the United States
- GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation) in the European Union
- Other applicable local healthcare privacy laws and regulations

The contributors and maintainers of this software are not responsible for
ensuring compliance with healthcare data protection laws. It is the
responsibility of the implementer to ensure proper security measures,
data encryption, access controls, and compliance with all applicable
healthcare privacy regulations.

## Disclaimer

This software is intended for educational and development purposes. Before using
this software in production environments handling real mental health data,
ensure proper security audits, compliance reviews, and professional oversight
are conducted.

Mental health is a serious matter. This software should never be used as a
substitute for professional mental health care, diagnosis, or treatment.